      <title>前出版商称黎智英利用《苹果日报》鼓励抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/lai-used-apple-daily-to-encourage-protest-former-publisher-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前香港媒体大亨黎智英在法庭上表示，他指示高管利用他的《苹果日报》鼓励人们参加抗议活动，并向政府施加压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/lai-used-apple-daily-to-encourage-protest-former-publisher-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:51:33 GMT</pubDate>
