    <item>
      <title>印度最大银行支持遏制“不健康”贷款增长的举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/india-s-biggest-bank-backs-move-to-curb-unhealthy-loan-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大银行的董事长表示，印度最近对无担保贷款的限制是遏制个人借贷“不健康增长”的正确举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/india-s-biggest-bank-backs-move-to-curb-unhealthy-loan-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:47:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及货币大幅贬值的押注因国际货币基金组织加大一揽子计划的希望而破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bets-on-big-fx-devaluation-in-egypt-crushed-as-government-nears-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年年初，随着埃及政府即将与国际货币基金组织达成协议以扩大救助计划规模，投资者纷纷抛售埃及货币大幅贬值的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bets-on-big-fx-devaluation-in-egypt-crushed-as-government-nears-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德：欧洲央行可能会在夏季降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/lagarde-ecb-will-likely-cut-rates-in-the-summer-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行可能会在夏季降息。当被问及这一举措是否会得到多数人的支持时，拉加德表示：“我想说这也有可能。”鉴于几位政策制定者已经表示了这一时机。她是在瑞士达沃斯世界经济论坛年会期间在彭博大厦发表上述言论的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/lagarde-ecb-will-likely-cut-rates-in-the-summer-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:44:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀加速，交易员认为英国央行降息幅度较小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/traders-aggressively-pare-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-cpi-quickens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示通胀10个月来首次意外上升后，交易员大幅削减了对英国央行降息的押注，英国债券大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/traders-aggressively-pare-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-cpi-quickens</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>太阳能电池板制造商因考虑关闭德国工厂而股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/swiss-solar-panel-maker-weighs-closing-german-unit-amid-us-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士太阳能电池板制造商梅耶博格科技股份公司 (Meyer Burger Technology AG) 表示可能关闭欧洲最大的生产基地之一并将重心转向美国，股价暴跌 47%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/swiss-solar-panel-maker-weighs-closing-german-unit-amid-us-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:20:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达沃斯直播：摩根大通仍在为华尔街招聘救济人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管华尔街一直在谈论裁员，但摩根大通表示已计划增加员工人数，而瑞银集团董事长则对影子银行发出警告，试图在世界经济论坛上转移监管机构的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
